"><span>Unlock the world of Apple.</span></h2><div class="SectionHeader_ctaWrapper__HJNTs"><ul class="SectionHeader_ctaList__luQ5v"><li class="SectionHeader_description__hZqOh MarcomSection_enhanced--initial__jX1gR"><a class="typography_bodyCopy__v_XbA StandardsLink_link__WcJoK StandardsLink_icon-wrapper__bIVCW" data-analytics-title="learn how apple devices work better together" href="/macos/continuity/"><span class="StandardsLink_copy__FvCj1"><span>Learn how Apple devices work better together</span></span><span class="StandardsLink_icon__rkBQJ StandardsLink_icon-after__RU8rf StandardsLink_icon-more__X5J7u"></span></a></li></ul></div></div><div class="responsive-content_responsiveContent__S1ntz"><div class="ImageAccordion_imageAccordionContainer__WaT9u AccordionSection_enhanced--initial__Mr3MV animationDefaults_noBuildIn__wAp_w"><ul class="ImageAccordion_accordion__vRgS6" role="list" aria-labelledby="accordion-section-12-header"><li class="ImageAccordion_accordionItem__jYIo_" role="listitem"><h3 class="ImageAccordion_accordionItemHeadline__bdCG0 typography_headline__zZkHA"><button class="ImageAccordion_accordionButton__qj7ql" aria-controls="accordion-item-0-tray" type="button" role="button" data-analytics-click="prop3:open accordion - mac and iphone" data-analytics-title="open accordion - mac and iphone" data-analytics-intrapage-link="" aria-expanded="true"><span class="ImageAccordion_accordionTitleText__6ouHq"><span>Mac and iPhone</span></span></button></h3><div id="accordion-item-0-tray" class="ImageAccordion_accordionTray__BHx_I"><div class="ImageAccordion_accordionContent__qFdLA"><div><p>Answer calls or messages from your iPhone directly on your Mac. See and control what’s on your iPhone from your Mac with iPhone Mirroring and Live Activities. Use Universal Clipboard to copy images, video, or text from your iPhone, then paste into another app on your nearby Mac. And thanks to iCloud, you can access your files from either your iPhone or your Mac. And so m⁠u⁠c⁠h⁠ ⁠m⁠o⁠r⁠e⁠.</p></div><div class="ImageAccordion_accordionItemImageContainer__3SNxX"><figure data-vp-w-large="" data-vp-h-large="" data-vp-w-medium="" data-vp-h-medium="" data-vp-w-small="" data-vp-h-small="" style="--vp-w-large:683;--vp-h-large:784;--vp-w-medium:683;--vp-h-medium:399;--vp-w-small:309;--vp-h-small:181;--vp-w-default:683;--vp-h-default:784" class="ResponsivePicture_responsive-picture__VWL7l responsive-picture-vp-layout-default--none responsive-picture__no-js ResponsivePicture_responsive-picture--no-load___9Rzr ResponsivePicture_responsive-picture--removed__vyAL_ ImageAccordion_accordionImage__bAFHA"><picture class="ResponsivePicture_responsive-picture__picture__jjeBP ResponsivePicture_responsive-picture__picture__js__PPGS5"><source srcSet="#, # 2x" width="309" height="181" media="(max-width: 734px)"/><source srcSet="#, # 2x" width="683" height="399" media="(max-width: 1068px)"/><source srcSet="#, # 2x" width="683" height="784"/><img alt="iPhone 16 Plus with text highlighted in the Notes app, 13-inch Macbook Air with a Keynote slide open, text from Notes app is visible on the slide
"/></picture><noscript><picture class="ResponsivePicture_responsive-picture__picture__jjeBP ResponsivePicture_responsive-picture__picture__no-js__Ma_sk"><source srcSet="/assets-www/en_WW/mac/03_image_accordion/small/mac_iphone_2e0e4641c.jpg, /assets-www/en_WW/mac/03_image_accordion/small/mac_iphone_8dbb98c8c_2x.jpg 2x" width="309" height="181" media="(max-width: 734px)"/><source srcSet="/assets-www/en_WW/mac/03_image_accordion/medium/mac_iphone_a0a10477e.jpg, /assets-www/en_WW/mac/03_image_accordion/medium/mac_iphone_8eaeabca4_2x.jpg 2x" width="683" height="399" media="(max-width: 1068px)"/><source srcSet="/assets-www/en_WW/mac/03_image_accordion/large/mac_iphone_c5e04dd47.jpg, /assets-www/en_WW/mac/03_image_accordion/large/mac_iphone_d50c6f239_2x.jpg 2x" width="683" height="784"/><img alt="iPhone 16 Plus with text highlighted in the Notes app, 13-inch Macbook Air with a Keynote slide open, text from Notes app is visible on the slide
"/></picture></noscript></figure></div></div></div></li><li class="ImageAccordion_accordionItem__jYIo_ ImageAccordion_collapsed__10ccw" role="listitem"><h3 class="ImageAccordion_accordionItemHeadline__bdCG0 typography_headline__zZkHA"><button class="ImageAccordion_accordionButton__qj7ql" aria-controls="accordion-item-1-tray" type="button" role="button" data-analytics-click="prop3:open accordion - mac and ipad" data-analytics-title="open accordion - mac and ipad" data-analytics-intrapage-link="" aria-expanded="false"><span class="ImageAccordion_accordionTitleText__6ouHq"><span>Mac and iPad</span></span></button></h3><div id="accordion-item-1-tray" class="ImageAccordion_accordionTray__BHx_I"><div class="ImageAccordion_accordionContent__qFdLA" inert="" aria-hidden="true"><div><p>Sketch on your iPad and have it appear instantly on your Mac. Or use your iPad as a second display, so you can work on one screen while you reference the other. You can even start something on your iPad — like a presentation or an email — and continue it on your Mac.</p></div><div class="ImageAccordion_accordionItemImageContainer__3SNxX"><figure data-vp-w-large="" data-vp-h-large="" data-vp-w-medium="" data-vp-h-medium="" data-vp-w-small="" data-vp-h-small="" style="--vp-w-large:707;--vp-h-large:784;--vp-w-medium:681;--vp-h-medium:288;--vp-w-small:308;--vp-h-small:131;--vp-w-default:707;--vp-h-default:784" class="ResponsivePicture_responsive-picture__VWL7l responsive-picture-vp-layout-default--none responsive-picture__no-js ResponsivePicture_responsive-picture--no-load___9Rzr ResponsivePicture_responsive-picture--removed__vyAL_ ImageAccordion_accordionImage__bAFHA"><picture class="ResponsivePicture_responsive-picture__picture__jjeBP ResponsivePicture_responsive-picture__picture__js__PPGS5"><source srcSet="#, # 2x" width="308" height="131" media="(max-width: 734px)"/><source srcSet="#, # 2x" width="681" height="288" media="(max-width: 1068px)"/><source srcSet="#, # 2x" width="707" height="784"/><img alt="An iPad next to a MacBook, both screens reflecting annotations on the same presentation in the Preview app"/></picture><noscript><picture class="ResponsivePicture_responsive-picture__picture__jjeBP ResponsivePicture_responsive-picture__picture__no-js__Ma_sk"><source srcSet="/assets-www/en_WW/mac/03_image_accordion/small/mac_ipad_06fc83d87.jpg, /assets-www/en_WW/mac/03_image_accordion/small/mac_ipad_e020d0868_2x.jpg 2x" width="308" height="131" media="(max-width: 734px)"/><source srcSet="/assets-www/en_WW/mac/03_image_accordion/medium/mac_ipad_46594c273.jpg, /assets-www/en_WW/mac/03_image_accordion/medium/mac_ipad_e696d365a_2x.jpg 2x" width="681" height="288" media="(max-width: 1068px)"/><source srcSet="/assets-www/en_WW/mac/03_image_accordion/large/mac_ipad_ea8018235.jpg, /assets-www/en_WW/mac/03_image_accordion/large/mac_ipad_e3dad78c7_2x.jpg 2x" width="707" height="784"/><img alt="An iPad next to a MacBook, both screens reflecting annotations on the same presentation in the Preview app"/></picture></noscript></figure></div></div></div></li><li class="ImageAccordion_accordionItem__jYIo_ ImageAccordion_collapsed__10ccw" role="listitem"><h3 class="ImageAccordion_accordionItemHeadline__bdCG0 typography_headline__zZkHA"><button class="ImageAccordion_accordionButton__qj7ql" aria-controls="accordion-item-2-tray" type="button" role="button" data-analytics-click="prop3:open accordion - mac and apple watch" data-analytics-title="open accordion - mac and apple watch" data-analytics-intrapage-link="" aria-expanded="false"><span class="ImageAccordion_accordionTitleText__6ouHq"><span>Mac and Apple Watch</span></span></button></h3><div id="accordion-item-2-tray" class="ImageAccordion_accordionTray__BHx_I"><div class="ImageAccordion_accordionContent__qFdLA" inert="" aria-hidden="true"><div><p>Automatically log in to your Mac when you’re wearing your Apple Watch with Auto Unlock. No password t⁠y⁠p⁠i⁠n⁠g⁠ ⁠r⁠e⁠q⁠u⁠i⁠r⁠e⁠d⁠.</p></div><div class="ImageAccordion_accordionIte